<plot>Mr. and Mrs. Runt are traveling on a train. Runt falls asleep in the smoking car, which is detached from the train. When Mrs. Runt discovers her husband is gone, Plump offers to help, and escorts her to her hotel. Runt arrives at the hotel, sees them together, and goes into a rage.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?496121</url></doc>
